  model: ImageModel,
  prompt: string | GenerateImagePrompt,
  n?: number,
  size?: string,
  aspectRatio?: string,
  seed?: number,
  providerOptions?: ProviderOptions,
  maxRetries?: number,
  abortSignal?: AbortSignal,
  headers?: Record<string, string>,
}: GenerateImageOptions): Promise<GenerateImageResult> {
  // Resolves model and validates
  // Handles batching for maxImagesPerCall
  // Implements retries
  // Converts responses to GenerateImageResult
}
```

### 13. Key Files to Reference

Absolute paths in this monorepo:

**Provider Base Types:**
- `/packages/provider/src/provider/v3/provider-v3.ts` - ProviderV3 interface
- `/packages/provider/src/image-model/v3/image-model-v3.ts` - ImageModelV3 interface
- `/packages/provider/src/image-model/v3/image-model-v3-call-options.ts` - Call parameters
- `/packages/provider/src/image-model/v3/image-model-v3-file.ts` - File type definition

**Example Implementations:**
- `/packages/openai/src/openai-provider.ts` - Full-featured provider
- `/packages/openai/src/image/openai-image-model.ts` - Complete image model
- `/packages/fal/src/fal-provider.ts` - Simpler provider (image-only)
- `/packages/deepinfra/src/deepinfra-image-model.ts` - Alternative API pattern

**Provider Utils:**
- `/packages/provider-utils/src/index.ts` - All exported utilities
- `/packages/provider-utils/src/post-to-api.ts` - HTTP request helpers
- `/packages/provider-utils/src/convert-image-model-file-to-data-uri.ts` - File conversion

**SDK Integration:**
- `/packages/ai/src/generate-image/generate-image.ts` - SDK usage of image models
- `/packages/ai/src/types/image-model.ts` - SDK-level type definitions

This comprehensive pattern enables rapid creation of new image generation providers with full type safety, standardized error handling, and seamless integration with the AI SDK.

